'''Bebo'''是一家美國社交网站，創設於2005年。

Bebo是“Blog Early, Blog Often”的縮寫<ref>{{cite web
    | url = http://uk.techcrunch.com/2008/03/13/aol-buys-bebo-for-850 m-in-cash/
    | title = AOL buys Bebo for $850m in cash
    | author = Butcher, Mike
    | date = 2008-03-08
    | publisher = [[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]
    | accessdate = 2008-09-20
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190215155213/http://uk.techcrunch.com/2008/03/13/aol-buys-bebo-for-850%C2%A0m-in-cash/
    | archive-date = 2019-02-15
    | dead-url = yes
    }}</ref>，用戶可以在個人資料頁發布博客、照片、音樂 ，影片和問卷調查。此外，用戶可添加朋友，並向他們發送消息，並更新他們的個人檔案，通知對自己的朋友。Bebo非常類似於其他社交網站，主要是[[Facebook|Facebook]]<ref name = "Michael and Xochi Birch">{{cite news
    | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2006/nov/04/socialnetworking.web20
    | title = Bebo, Michael and Xochi Birch
    | author = Burkeman, Oliver
    | date = 2006-11-04
    | publisher = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]
    | accessdate = 2010-06-14
    | location = London
    | archive-date = 2010-04-07
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100407101220/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2006/nov/04/socialnetworking.web20
    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref>。

2005年1月Michael Birch與其夫人Xochi Birch在其住所於[[舊金山|舊金山]]創立Bebo。

2007年7月Bebo访客数量首次超過[[Myspace|Myspace]]，成为英国最受欢迎的社交网站。2008年3月美國時代華納子公司[[AOL|AOL]]宣佈以8.5億收購Bebo<ref>{{cite news
    | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/7294174.stm
    | title = AOL acquires Bebo social network
    | date = March 13, 2008
    | publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]]
    | accessdate = 2008-03-13
    | archive-date = 2008-03-15
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080315021921/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/7294174.stm
    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref><ref>{{cite web
    | url = http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/ea66262a-f0f8-11dc-a91a-0000779fd2ac.html
