    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref>。2010年4月又計劃出售或關閉此網站<ref>{{cite web
    | url = http://www.marketwatch.com/story/aol-pulls-plug-on-bebo-social-networking-effort-2010-04-06
    | title = AOL pulls plug on Bebo social networking effort
